# A kanji ghost character (Japanese: [[w:ja:幽霊漢字|幽霊漢字]] ''yūrei kanji'', mistaken character which is registered in character code for Japanese, JIS X 0208); composed of the [[弓]] radical and [[哥]]. Likely to be an error of [[彊]].<ref>Naokazu Hiruma, [http://www.asahi.com/special/kotoba/archive2015/moji/2011082400019.html {{lang|ja|大正十二年の幽霊文字}}], ''The Asahi''</ref>
